    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the serious driver is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering exceptional induction notes through its individual throttle bodies and precise timing via the Double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 chassis harmonics. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension kinematics remain tight and the throttle mapping is razor-sharp, making this a prime candidate for a dedicated B-road machine.",
